### Specific statistics

We can also explore specific statistics

The penguins split by species show a specific relationship between
weight and flipper length, where the Adelie female penguins are the
lighest and have the shortest flippers.


::: {.cell hash='penguin-report_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_c67e4cbdb75dfeabae429df7c6963f46'}

```{.r .cell-code}
penguins %>% 
  group_by(species, sex) %>% 
  summarize(
    n = n(), 
    weight = mean(body_mass_g, na.rm = TRUE),
    flipper_length = mean(flipper_length_mm, na.rm = TRUE)
    ) %>% 
  arrange(desc(weight))
```

